---
title: Falafel and Tomato Flatbreads with Ful Medames-Inspired Stew
description: These Middle-Eastern-style flatbreads are the perfect handheld meal, stuffed with pickled radishes, filling falafels, dilly hummus and juicy tomatoes. A side of savoury ful medames-style kidney bean stew rounds out this hearty meal.
